en.name: Name
en.single_refersh_warning: Because the data used are all randomly generated, so every time the page is refreshed, the data will be reset, so when url with id refresh, can not get data. It is no problem to refresh with id in the real environment.

zh-CN.name: 名字
zh-CN.single_refersh_warning: 因为所用数据均是随机生成的，所以每次刷新的时候数据都会重置，所以导致url中带id的时候刷新拿不到数据。如果在真实环境中，带id刷新是没有问题的。
